    <section_number>58</section_number>
    <catch_line>Cities And Towns; Limitation On Purchasing Powers</catch_line>
    <order_by>58</order_by>
    <text>
        No city or town shall pay a bill incurred by any official thereof for wines, liquors or cigars.
    </text>
